You use these for the Potions assignment.

48
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:10,270
<i>What was with that
dramatic display just now?</i>

49
00:04:12,020 --> 00:04:13,640
A mandragora.

50
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:19,020
