102
00:07:15,870 --> 00:07:16,950
'Kay.

103
00:07:16,950 --> 00:07:18,450
Stir well.

104
00:07:18,450 --> 00:07:19,410
'Kay.

105
00:07:19,580 --> 00:07:21,540
