BA-YUMMY

109
00:07:26,170 --> 00:07:27,670
<i>Why is this!?</i>

110
00:07:28,050 --> 00:07:30,090
<i>I watched him from start to finish.</i>

111
00:07:30,090 --> 00:07:32,800
<i>When did it become a cream puff!?</i>

112
