277
00:17:25,060 --> 00:17:27,730
You really are wonderful.

278
00:17:35,860 --> 00:17:40,700
<i>With my magic, I can make anyone
even slightly attracted to me fall in love.</i>

279
00:17:41,160 --> 00:17:43,870
