284
00:17:59,180 --> 00:18:00,760
<i>What? That's impossible.</i>

285
00:18:01,260 --> 00:18:04,770
<i>There's never been a man
who hasn't fallen under my spell.</i>

286
00:18:05,020 --> 00:18:09,770
